      <akn:section eId="sec_31_4448">
        <akn:num>31-4448</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Merger or consolidation — Procedures before voting.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-4448_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p></akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-4448_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Written notice shall be delivered at least 20 days before the meeting, either personally or by mail, to each shareholder, member, or policyholder.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-4448_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The notice shall state the place, the time, and the purpose of the meeting, and a copy or a summary of the plan of merger or of consolidation shall be delivered with the notice.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-4448_d">
      <akn:num>(d)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The notice shall also summarize dissenting shareholders’ rights under § 31-4450.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
